HEADWORD: Restore
<hw>Re*store"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Restoration.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Spenser.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

